different markets,

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:30.400
we actually look
at which characters

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:33.380
and which packages makes
more sense for that reason.

00:07:33.380 --> 00:07:34.900
So we do outside pricing.

00:07:34.900 --> 00:07:39.550
We do tailor it culturally,
too, for the market.

00:07:39.550 --> 00:07:41.650
RAJ AJRAWAT: So taking
that discussion now,

00:07:41.650 --> 00:07:45.010
I'd actually like to transition
