to say this instead.

00:10:39.912 --> 00:10:41.620
So it's a good check
on a lot of the work

00:10:41.620 --> 00:10:44.050
that they're doing in terms
of approaching those markets.

00:10:44.050 --> 00:10:46.240
And it's ideally
somewhat lightweight

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:48.250
in terms of leveraging
those resources,

00:10:48.250 --> 00:10:51.502
