00:11:58.180 --> 00:11:59.680
Is this like a
financial relationship,

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.810
or is it just purely research,
or how is that structured?

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:02.590
MARK PANELO: Pure research.

00:12:02.590 --> 00:12:04.490
I mean, we're partnering
with universities.

00:12:04.490 --> 00:12:06.170
There's a prize
